|type = |director = Somshubhra |vice_chancellor = |city = [[Kolkata]] |state = [[West Bengal]] |country = India |campus = |affiliations = |website = {{URL|http://www.stmkolkata.org//}} }} [[File:Calcutta School of Tropical Medicine - 108 Chittaranjan Avenue - Kolkata 2014-10-30 0184-0189.tif|thumb|Calcutta School of Tropical Medicine, Kolkata. <small>October 2014.</small>]] '''Calcutta School of Tropical Medicine''' (CSTM) is a medical institute from [[Kolkata]], [[India]] dedicated in the field of [[tropical disease]].<ref>{{cite book|last=David Arnold|title=Science, Technology and Medicine in Colonial India|date=2000|publisher=Cambridge University Press|isbn=9780521563192|page=198|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=7bAxnPwOMd8C&pg=PA198&dq=calcutta+school+of+tropical+medicine&hl=en&sa=X&ei=MwVUU67XG4WIrge__YCYBA&ved=0CGAQ6AEwBw#v=onepage&q=calcutta%20school%20of%20tropical%20medicine&f=false}}</ref> It was established in 1914 by [[Leonard Rogers]] (1868-1962) of the Indian Medical Service, professor of pathology at the [[Calcutta Medical College]].<ref>{{cite book|last=Uma Dasgupta|title=Science and Modern India: An Institutional History, C. 1784-1947|date=2011|publisher=Pearson Education India|isbn=9788131728185|page=591|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=lrx3wLz4itkC&pg=PA591&dq=calcutta+school+of+tropical+medicine&hl=en&sa=X&ei=MwVUU67XG4WIrge__YCYBA&ved=0CFYQ6AEwBQ#v=onepage&q=calcutta%20school%20of%20tropical%20medicine&f=false}}</ref> It was, till 2003, affiliated with the [[University of Calcutta]]. Now it is under the [[West Bengal University of Health Sciences]].
Prominent researchers like [[Upendranath Brahmachari|U. N. Bramhachari]], [[Ronald Ross]], [[Rabindra Nath Chaudhuri]],<ref name="Deceased Fellow">{{cite web | url=http://insaindia.org.in/deceaseddetail.php?id=N500158 | title=Deceased Fellow | publisher=Indian National Science Academy | date=2016 | accessdate=6 July 2016 }}{{dead link|date=December 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref> [[Ram Narayan Chakravarti]]<ref name="Deceased Fellow1">{{cite web | url=http://www.insaindia.org/deceaseddetail.php?id=N560139 | title=Deceased Fellow | publisher=Indian National Science Academy | date=2016 | accessdate=2 April 2016 }}{{dead link|date=December 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref> and [[Jyoti Bhusan Chatterjea]] worked in this institute.<ref>{{cite web|title=History of CSTM|url=http://www.stmkolkata.org/history.html|work=stmkolkata.org|accessdate=20 April 2014}}</ref>
